verdict.key_information_requested:
Detailed customer contracts and renewal terms to assess SaaS revenue visibility; 
Manufacturing capacity plans and supply chain risk mitigation strategies;
Product roadmap and anticipated R&D pipeline for next 3 years;
Regulatory approvals status and timelines in priority international markets;
Competitive landscape analysis with pricing strategies and win/loss data;
Detailed unit economics separating hardware and SaaS margins and customer acquisition costs.
